        <Parent_String>glassworking processes and techniques [300236662], glassworking and glassworking processes and techniques [300236660], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
